<ab facs="#facs_554_r1l13">den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> burger von ſölcher klag vnd <expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_554_r1l14">cʒu vvyſen / So vvolt <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_554_r1l15">von <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>Swarcʒemberg<ex>er</ex></expan> . des rehten vor <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_554_r1l16">Rete <expan>ſchıcke<ex>n</ex></expan> geholffen . darauff vvir auch alſo <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
