<del rend="strikethrough">vnd </del> vnd das reht darümb von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_554_r1l20">dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>Swarcʒemberg<ex>er</ex></expan> vor <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> gnaden Reten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_554_r1l21">ʒenemen / Daſſelb auch der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> . als Er vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_554_r1l22"><expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> hat / getan . Vnd <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>Swarcʒemberg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_554_r1l23">mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> rehten vor <expan>ewre<ex>n</ex></expan> Reten gerehtfertigt hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_554_r1l24">Darnach ſey derſelb ~ <expan>Swarcʒemberg<ex>er</ex></expan> her gen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_554_r1l26"><expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> kumen . vnd hab Jn hie vor geriht 
<add><ab facs="#facs_554_r1l25">widerümb </ab></add> <expan>angeſproch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_554_r1l27">Vnd gerehtfertigt / als das <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> gerihtsbuch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_554_r1l28"> <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd begriffen 
<del rend="strikethrough">iſt </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_554_line_1592205263366_3231">ſey </ab></add> / Darüber ſey nü der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_554_r1l29"><expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> ~ <expan>Swarʒcemberg<ex>er</ex></expan> aber ʒugefaren vnd hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_554_r1l30">geſchickt / daʒ derſelb ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> geladen worden ſeẏ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_554_r1l31">für das gerichte des freyenſtuls cʒum frygenhain </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_554_r1l34">vnder der lẏnden 
<add><ab facs="#facs_554_r1l32">in dem land cʒu heſſen </ab></add> ſich cʒu <expan>verantvv<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>
