<del rend="strikethrough">ſchıcken vnd </del> ernſtlıch beſtellen wöllet / daʒ Er ſchıck </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_554_r1l42">ſölch <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> klag vnd <expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vor dem 
