                        czu eren und zu gefallen <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> weisten, <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
