<add>niht gewönlich gewesen ist</add>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz
                        ir durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>obgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <add>dem ewren</add>
<expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan>
